      "updated_at": "2016-07-29T05:08:56Z",
      "body": "Yes you are right grid layout is awesome, absolutely.\n\nSupport this feature means we need some consideration and preparations more:\n1. Know-how for front-end engineers, not very much developers familiar with grid layout today.\n2. Efficiency, wide and strong enough implementation in mobile browsers http://caniuse.com/css-grid and native view (css-layout)\n3. The simplification of tech design of a framework/solution.\n\nMaybe the research should be continued as anyway anyone like. And the discussion could be made again in a more appropriate time when the stuff above come true.\n\nThanks.\n"
