      "updated_at": "2016-07-29T19:54:05Z",
      "body": "Thanks, it is good to have this on the radar. CSS-Grid is something to anticipate with certainty and learning it for frontend engineers is very easy, there are already numerous tutorials. In addition frontend engineers will drop what they know as soon as they see how incredibly efficient layout has become with CSS-Grid.\n\nLikely an enhancement to the CSS-Layout library is in order ASAP. Maybe a translation of CSS-Grid semantics to something the CSS-Layout requires is a start.\n"
